        Fired every time an island event occurs. For developers who just want one event and will use an enum to track the reason
        Parameters:
        island - - the island involved in the event
        playerUUID - - the player's UUID involved in the event
        admin - - true if this is due to an admin event
        location - - location of event
        reason - - see getReason()
